# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment variables for RCCG Overcomers House Cwmbran
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development, and set the same values
# in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables for production.
# Only NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL is currently read by the app — the rest are
# optional placeholders for integrations described in the README, and do
# nothing until that integration is wired up.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Required ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Canonical, fully-qualified site URL (no trailing slash). Used for canonical
# tags, Open Graph URLs, the sitemap, and robots.txt. Set this to your real
# production domain so SEO metadata is correct.
#   Production example: https://rccgcwmbran.co.uk
#   Preview/Vercel:     https://<your-project>.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://rccgcwmbran.co.uk


# ── Optional: Analytics (not wired up yet) ───────────────────────────────────
# Google Analytics 4 measurement ID. Only takes effect once the GA script is
# added in src/app/layout.tsx (see "Analytics" in README.md).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX


# ── Form delivery (email submissions) ────────────────────────────────────────
# The Plan-a-visit / Prayer / Connect forms POST to /api/contact, which emails
# the submission to the church via Resend (https://resend.com).
#
# Without RESEND_API_KEY the form still "succeeds" for the visitor, but the
# submission is only logged to the server console (not emailed) — fine for
# local dev. Set these in Vercel to deliver real emails:
#
#   RESEND_API_KEY      — API key from resend.com
#   CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL  — a VERIFIED sender on your domain in Resend,
#                         e.g. "Overcomers House <noreply@rccgcwmbran.co.uk>"
#   CONTACT_EMAIL       — inbox that receives submissions
#                         (optional; defaults to the email in src/data/site.ts)
#
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=Overcomers House <noreply@rccgcwmbran.co.uk>
# CONTACT_EMAIL=hello@rccgcwmbran.co.uk


# ── Note on content (NOT env vars) ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Church details — name, address, phone, email, service times, giving URL,
# livestream URL, and social links — are edited directly in:
#   src/data/site.ts
# They are intentionally not environment variables.
